            "description": "<p><em><strong>Notes</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>Status: PKWT 12 months under Sigmatech (extendable)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>Placement: Fintech Industry (WFO, Central Jakarta)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>Salary: 10.5 mio gross + 250.000 transport allowance</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>Benefit: Laptop provided, BPJS Kesehatan &amp; Ketenagakerjaan, Kompensasi UUCK 100%, THR Prorate</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Job Description: </strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>Summary:</strong></em></p>\n<p>As a Data Analyst &amp; Insight, you will transform raw data into meaningful stories. You will be responsible for interpreting data, creating dashboards, and providing actionable recommendations to help the business make smarter decisions.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></em></p>\n<ul><li>Data Analysis: Clean, process, and analyze large datasets to identify trends, patterns, and anomalies.</li>\n  <li>Reporting: Design and maintain automated dashboards (e.g., Tableau, Power BI, or Looker) to track key business metrics.</li>\n  <li>Business Insights: Translate data findings into clear, actionable insights for stakeholders (Product, Marketing, or Management).</li>\n  <li>Data Integrity: Ensure data accuracy and consistency by working closely with the Data Engineering team.</li>\n  <li>Problem Solving: Support various departments by answering business questions through ad-hoc data deep-dives.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Requirements</strong></em></p>\n<ul><li>Education: Bachelor’s degree in Mathematics, Statistics, Computer Science, Economics, or a related field.</li>\n  <li>Experience: Minimum [X] years of experience in a data-driven role (Experience in Fintech/E-commerce is a plus).</li>\n  <li>Strong proficiency in SQL (a must).</li>\n  <li>Experience with Data Visualization tools (e.g., Tableau, Power BI, or Google Data Studio).</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge of Python or R for data manipulation.</li>\n  <li>Analytical Thinking: Exceptional ability to analyze complex problems and provide data-backed solutions.</li>\n  <li>Attention to Detail: High precision in data handling and reporting.</li>\n</ul>",
